        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 7. Scanning electron micrographs of the protoconch sculpture in Plagiodontes weyenberghii weyenberghii (A–D) and Plagiodontes weyenberghii minor (E–H). (A,B) Protoconch and first teleoconch whorls; (C) close-up of (A) showing spiral lines crossing axial striae and medial depression. (D) Teleoconch sculpture showing waved intercostular lines. (E,F) Protoconch and first teleoconch whorls; (G) close-up of (E) showing spiral lines crossing axial striae. (H) Teleoconch sculpture." ;
